## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-102">使用带有 <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> 或 <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 来暂停情节提要。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or a <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to pause a Storyboard.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 仅影响处于活动状态的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> （在 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> 启动后）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-104">若要控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>，<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 必须引用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>控制的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-104">To control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls that <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-105">有关示例，请参阅[如何：使用事件触发器来控制演示图板](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-105">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="beginning-a-paused-animation"></a><span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-106">开始暂停的动画</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-106">Beginning a Paused Animation</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-107">如果 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 操作在暂停后触发，则会显示 "继续" 和 "重新启动"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-107">When a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action is triggered after it has been paused, it appears to resume and restart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-108">但实际上不会发生这种情况： <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 操作实际上会将自身替换为未暂停版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-108">That's not what actually happens, however: the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action actually replaces itself with an unpaused version.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-109">每次触发 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 操作时，都会为其情节提要创建时钟对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-109">Each time a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> action is triggered, clock objects are created for its storyboard.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-110">这些时钟会分配给它们的动画属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-110">These clocks are distributed to the properties they animate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a0b2f-111">因此，当再次触发 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 时，它不会重新启动其时钟，而是将其替换为新的时钟。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0b2f-111">So, when a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is triggered again, it doesn't restart its clocks, it replaces them with new clocks.</span></span>  
  
